moji\" />"},{"pid":"84b564ba74e16920e5844429c86163e2d179531a","tid":117032,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"永登蒲好，Times Square 附近有紅燈區"},{"pid":"75af35cc6fac7daf7cd17b8be71fbfbc688bc534","tid":117032,"uid":21201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同女去定點？</blockquote><br />\n同女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3678baa1664f9d1d5915542a5a04c9f9015b153","tid":117032,"uid":21201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永登浦呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嘅價錢差唔多啦<br />\n依個時候應該大風到痴孖筋<br />\n特別明洞弘大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想去樂天世界嘅話，唔記得咩信用卡有折<br />\n不如你list想去/會去嘅地方出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見3月尾天氣都係十幾度左右，仲諗住去水上樂園，會唔會凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行程未plan好，不過會去著韓服，弘大，梨大買衫褲，明洞買化妝品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能會行汝夷島。主要想問下有咩值得推介景點and食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb585ab2650ab5c43f25a83415cee3ab156939b8","tid":117032,"uid":21201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>週末去光化門廣場果頭都幾多野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前果次去有書法同世越號既booth 想睇多啲當地文化可以去下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期六弘大有free market 都係賣下手作仔咁 都值得去下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> free market得星期六先有？"},{"pid":"edaf64617c6c6e27bf205f6540